 devant; aplatirz2; 51; 5; x4b4; b4b4; c5b4z2; czcxz0; x4x4z0;  
 b0ab; i; 2; naep2; 1; b0; ab;
 axe; aplatirz; 51; 4; x1b0;  b0ab; cxcz; x1x1z1;
 derriere;  i; 51; 9; b0b4; b4b4; b3b4z2; b3b3; b2b3z1; b2b2; b1b2z2; cxcy; b0ab; 
 entaille1; i;         51; 4; b2b2; b2d2z2; d2d2; b2d2z1;
 entaille2; aplatirz1; 51; 4; d3b3z1; b3b3; d3b3z2; d3d3;
@; 

